I would take her on
the town, but that's just me.

40
00:03:28,125 --> 00:03:30,750
Oh.
She dumped ya, huh?

41
00:03:35,958 --> 00:03:39,458
Who, Deunan?
I saw her earlier today.

42
00:03:39,541 --> 00:03:40,541
You did?

43
00:03:40,625 --> 00:03:41,750
Yes.

44
00:03:41,833 --> 00:03:43,583
There was another
bioroid suicide

45
00:03:43,666 --> 00:03:45,458
in the Ladon River district.

46
00:03:45,541 --> 00:03:49,041
I was asked to visit the scene
as a Tartaros Center observer.

47
