dead two times over!

68
00:05:09,333 --> 00:05:12,208
Karl, would you let her
take a break already?

69
00:05:12,291 --> 00:05:14,208
How many times
do I have to tell you?

70
00:05:14,291 --> 00:05:15,541
Watch your back!

71
00:05:15,625 --> 00:05:17,291
No one else will do it for you!

72
00:05:17,375 --> 00:05:18,375
That's enough Karl!

73
00:05:18,458 --> 00:05:19,666
What the hell are you doing?

74
00:05:19,750 --> 00:05:22,166
The poor girl can't
take much more of this!

75
00:05:23,166 --> 00:05:25,083
Is something wrong?

76
00:05:25,166 --> 00:05:27,250
Briareos!

77
00:05:27,333 --> 00:05:28,458
Deunan.

78
00:05:29,458 --> 00:05:31,041
Earlier you-- 

79
00:05:31,125 --> 00:05:32,791
I what?

80
00:05:32,875 --> 00:05:35,000
Uh, never mind.

81
00:05:36,500 --> 00:05:38,625
You can be such a weirdo.

82
00:05:43,250 --> 00:05:46,000
She's probably just
getting it overhauled.

83
00:05:46,083 --> 00:05:47,625
If she was in the
Ladon River district,

84
00:05:47,708 --> 00:05:50,083
I bet she took it to Ceryneia.

85
00:05:50,166 --> 00:05:51,750
Ceryneia?

86
